title: Ground News - Clark announces she will be entering 2024 WNBA Draft
text:
Summary by TSN Iowa Hawkeyes' Caitlin Clark announced on X Thursday that this season will be her last and she will be entering the 2024 WNBA Draft. Share menu 9 Articles 9 Articles All Left Center Right
Sporting News Media Conglomerate: Access Industries Caitlin Clark enters 2024 WNBA Draft: Why Iowa star is passing up fifth year with Hawkeyes to go pro The 22-year-old decided to forego her fifth year of college eligibility and enter the 2024 WNBA Draft, where she is the projected No. 1 overall pick.
